1:00:04.726 --> 1:00:11.441
<i>Question everything that you're used to</i>

1:00:12.066 --> 1:00:14.736
<i>Isn't it nice to see yourself</i>

1:00:14.819 --> 1:00:17.322
<i>At the beginning?</i>

1:00:17.405 --> 1:00:20.908
<i>You, without any scars</i>

1:00:20.992 --> 1:00:27.540
<i>Or pain?</i>

1:00:54.442 --> 1:00:56.986
<i>Fear is essentially</i>

1:00:57.070 --> 1:01:00.281
<i>A shadow you grow within yourself</i>

1:01:01.240 --> 1:01:06.871
<i>They are things</i>
<i>That may disappear in a second</i>

1:01:06.954 --> 1:01:12.168
<i>Lift your head up when the road is blocked</i>

1:01:12.251 --> 1:01:17.256
<i>Look at the sky</i>

1:01:17.340 --> 1:01:22.095
<i>That doesn't need roads</i>

1:01:23.554 --> 1:01:26.557
<i>Don't fall for the lies</i>

1:01:27.058 --> 1:01:30.061
<i>That whisper and tell you to crouch</i>

1:01:30.645 --> 1:01:35.566
<i>Those dead words of darkness</i>

1:01:36.776 --> 1:01:39.195
<i>Must have hurt</i>

1:01:39.278 --> 1:01:41.739
<i>But you are stronger now</i>

1:01:41.823 --> 1:01:47.912
<i>Believe in yourself</i>

1:01:57.380 --> 1:02:01.008
<i>Choose the way you want to go</i>

1:02:01.092 --> 1:02:04.554
<i>You're already there</i>

1:02:04.637 --> 1:02:10.893
<i>Pick the brightest smile and practice</i>

1:02:12.103 --> 1:02:14.689
<i>Isn't it nice to see yourself</i>

1:02:14.772 --> 1:02:17.400
<i>In this moment</i>

